Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 650
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "# roundtable — multi-agent Claude Code debate"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "npx roundtable --help"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "# Built-in panels: debate / code-review / microservices"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "npx roundtable debate --topic 'Monorepo vs polyrepo?' -m haiku -r 1"
Sleep 800ms
Enter

Sleep 45s
